      "code": "def strip_diacritics(s):\n    # remove Arabic diacritics and tatweel\n    arabic_diacritics = re.compile(r'[\\u064B-\\u065F\\u06D6-\\u06ED]')\n    s = re.sub(arabic_diacritics, '', s)\n    s = s.replace('ـ','')\n    return s\n\ndef normalize_ar(s):\n    s = s or ''\n    s = strip_diacritics(s)\n    s = s.replace('أ','ا').replace('إ','ا').replace('آ','ا').replace('ٱ','ا')\n    s = s.replace('ى','ي')\n    s = s.replace('ؤ','و').replace('ئ','ي')\n    s = s.replace('ة','ه')\n    s = re.sub(r'[^\\w\\s]', ' ', s)\n    s = re.sub(r'\\s+',' ', s).strip().lower()\n    return s\n\nquery = \"وَمَنْ يَقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا\"\nnorm_query = normalize_ar(query)\nmatches = []\nfor v in quran:\n    if norm_query in normalize_ar(v['ayah_text']):\n        matches.append(v)\nlen(matches), [(m['surah_name'], m['ayah_id']) for m in matches[:10]]",
